prerequesites
npm init -y
npm install electron 
npm install electron --save-dev --registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com


Features Now Implemented 

Your Browser Activity Monitoring team now covers:

1.Fullscreen Enforcement

Start exam → fullscreen
Detect exit
Force fullscreen again

2.Keyboard Shortcut Monitoring

Blocks:
Ctrl+C
Ctrl+V
Ctrl+A
Ctrl+T
Ctrl+N
Ctrl+P
Ctrl+S
F12

3.Developer Tools Detection

Detects:
DevTools opened
Console usage attempts
Window resizing due to DevTools

4.Multiple Browser Instance Detection

Detects:
Same exam open in multiple windows
Uses localStorage

Action:

Log violation
Show warning

